text: Morimus assamensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1936. It is known from Tibet and China.BioLib.cz - Morimus assamensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1936
title: Morimus assamensis
